@startuml MyAIStorybook_Activity_Diagram
title MyAIStorybook - Activity Diagram: Complete Story Generation Workflow

|User|
start
:Enter story prompt;
:Select generation options\n(images, mode);
:Click "Weave Magic";

|Frontend|
:Send generation request\nto backend;

|Backend - PromptAgent|
:Receive prompt;
:Validate prompt format;

if (Prompt valid?) then (yes)
    :Enhance prompt\nwith details;
else (no)
    :Return error message;
    |Frontend|
    :Display error to user;
    stop
endif

|Backend - DirectorAgent|
:Initialize multi-agent\npipeline;

|Backend - WriterAgent|
:Generate story structure;
:Create title and setting;
:Develop characters;
:Write 3 scenes;
:Generate image descriptions;

|Backend - ReviewerAgent|
:Review story draft;
:Check age-appropriateness;
:Evaluate narrative coherence;
:Assess educational value;
:Generate feedback;

|Backend - EditorAgent|
:Apply reviewer feedback;
:Refine story text;
:Ensure JSON validity;
:Generate PDF export;

|Backend|
if (Generate images?) then (yes)
    |Backend - ImageAgent|
    fork
        :Generate Scene 1 image;
        :txt2img (512x512);
        :img2img upscale;
    fork again
        :Generate Scene 2 image;
        :txt2img (512x512);
        :img2img upscale;
    fork again
        :Generate Scene 3 image;
        :txt2img (512x512);
        :img2img upscale;
    end fork
    :Save all images;
else (no)
    :Skip image generation;
endif

|Backend - EvaluationAgent|
:Evaluate story quality\n(background process);
note right
    Runs asynchronously
    without blocking response
end note

|Backend|
:Save story to database;
:Prepare response JSON;
:Return story data;

|Frontend|
:Receive story data;
:Initialize story display;
:Render page navigation;
:Load images (if available);

|User|
:View generated story;
:Navigate through pages;

if (Want to chat with character?) then (yes)
    :Select character;
    :Start chat conversation;
    |Backend - ChatbotAgent|
    :Generate character responses;
    |User|
    :Continue chatting;
else (no)
endif

if (Want to export?) then (yes)
    :Download PDF;
else (no)
endif

stop

@enduml
